Text.Value: What were you doing down here?
*The corpse remains silent. It does not know.*

EditorData.logicalname: DOESN'T KNOW ANSWER - DELETE IF NOT NEEDED

Text.Value: Did Sarin have a parasite in her head? A tadpole?
Cult... took Sarin's mind... so we... took her head...
*The corpse does not stir. It will answer no more questions.*
Said I lost... my mind... then lost... his voice...
Sarin... Bareki... me... no better... thieves...
*The spell's power wanes. You can ask no more questions.*
*The corpse seems willing to speak - but not to its killer.*

Synopsis: Speak with dead with the Fire Wizard in the Sewers. He was pursued by the Absolutist and flead to the sewers for safety. We can hint at the position of the Abandoned Cistern and Minsc in there too.
